Package de.upb.crc901.proseco.command

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Command
    Command, interface for Command Pattern
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BootUpInternalBenchmarkServiceCommand
    BootUpInternalBenchmarkServiceCommand, finds the internal benchmark service (benchmarkService.bat) executable file of the selected prototype, and starts it as a process.
    CleanExecutionEnvironmentCommand
    CleanExecutionEnvironmentCommand cleans up the execution directory by deleting all the created files in the ExecutionEnvironment, if the FINAL_CLEAN_UP flag is active.
    ExecuteGroundingRoutineCommand
    ExecuteGroundingRoutineCommand, finds the grounding routine (groundingroutine.bat) executable file of the selected prototype, and starts it as a process.
    ExecuteStrategiesCommand
    ExecuteStrategiesCommand, searches for strategy subfolders and forking a new process for each strategy.
    GetPrototypeDirectoryCommand
    GetPrototypeDirectoryCommand, searches for a prototype with the given name and returns it directory as File.
    InitializeExecutionEnvironmentCommand
    InitializeExecutionEnvironmentCommand, initializes the ExecutionEnvironment by creating a copy of the selected prototype skeleton.
    MovePlaceholderFilesToSourceCommand
    MovePlaceholderFilesToSourceCommand, moves all placeholder files created by the winning strategy to the source folder as inputs for the grounding routine.
    ShutDownInternalBenchmarkServiceCommand
    ShutDownInternalBenchmarkServiceCommand, after execution of the strategies completed it waits for internal benchmark service (benchmarkService.bat) to terminate.
    WaitForStrategiesCommand
    WaitForStrategiesCommand, waits (busy waiting) for the processes to terminate that have been started to execute the different strategies.
